==Demographics==
The median age of people in Falmouth is 34.1. Falmouth has a larger male population 53% of the population being male, while 47% is female. 90% of the people who in Falmouth are White, with the next most populous ethnicity being the 8% Hispanic population.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Census profile: Falmouth, MI |url=https://censusreporter.org/profiles/16000US2627320-falmouth-mi/ |access-date=2024-09-27 |website=Census Reporter |language=en}}</ref>{{US Census population
